{"title":"部队过山村","authors":["韩瑞亭"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":2,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"部队过山村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩瑞亭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳早西沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"部队进山村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命令一个传一个："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小心，不要出声音！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“吱扭”一声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慌了过路人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看我，我看他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——呀，原来是老乡打开门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘掌灯倚门站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大爷在石阶上摇手巾："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“过门不入算失礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快来擦把汗，洗洗尘。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暖暖的火炕热米汤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花生栗子一大盆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大爷下了冲击令："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不动嘴不许出门！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当年队伍打鬼子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三次进村家不进；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任务急，情况紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"委屈了大娘一片心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今的娃没变样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作风还像八路军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年前的声音没改调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听脚步就知道是你们！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴心话如同炉中火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧化了寒冷暖热了心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡唱三遍再上路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大爷大娘挥着白手巾……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}